<topic title="Subscription component (Watch this?)">
	<section title="What you can do on this page">
		<p>The subscription (Watch this?) component lets you subscribe to Mingle to view project changes as they happen. 
			Mingle provides feeds or emails based on the Filter history you have selected (i.e. the criteria that determines what Mingle is currently displaying on the History tab).</p>
